{
  "texts": [
    "In the context of token classification tasks, we conducted a comprehensive comparison between SK-Tuning and traditional tuning methods.",
    "We utilized two benchmark datasets, namely Wikiann and Conll03, both featuring token-level labels.",
    "Our primary objective was to analyze the convergence behavior, measured in terms of loss reduction, as training steps progressed.",
    "Figure 3 visually presents the convergence trajectories for SK-Tuning and traditional methods.",
    "Notably, we observed a remarkable disparity in the convergence speed between these approaches."
  ]
}